@desc Email, chat with, or phone a contact.

To email, chat with or phone someone in $app(Contacts):

[steps]
* Select the contact from your contact list.

* Press on the $em(detail) that you want to use. For example, to
  email your contact, press the email address.

* The corresponding application will be launched using the contactâ€™s
  details.

[note]
  If there is no available application for the detail that you wish to
  use, you will not be able to select it.
